<h1>Order Cancellation</h1>
<p>Dear <%= @user.full_name || "User" %>,</p>
<p>Your order #<%= @order.id %> has been successfully canceled at <%= @timestamp %>. Below are the details of the canceled item:</p>

<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;">Book Image</th>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;">Book Name</th>
      <th style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;">Quantity</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; text-align: center;">
        <img src="<%= @order.book.book_image %>" alt="<%= @order.book.book_name %>" style="max-width: 100px; height: auto;" />
      </td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;"><%= @order.book.book_name %></td>
      <td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;"><%= @order.quantity %></td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>If you did not request this cancellation, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
<p>Thank you,<br>The Bookstore Team</p>